<HEADLINE> German Air Force Grounds All Tornado Jets </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, January 27 (Xinhua) -- The German Air Force has
temporarily grounded its Tornado fighter jets amid suspicions that
the crash of such a warplane off the northern German coast a week
ago may have been caused by a technical defect, the German Defense
Ministry announced Tuesday.
</P>
