way. Over the past few days, only small parts of the wreckage have
been found.
</P>
<P>
The Tornado crashed in the Atlantic near the northern German
island of Borkum last Tuesday after returning from a training
mission in the Netherlands. Two soldiers on board, including the
pilot, were killed in the accident. 
