revive the nation's economy but it would take some time to
materialize and require the cooperation of the people especially
the business community.
</P>
<P>
"If we don't do anything that could cause the country to suffer
losses just to reap instant benefits for ourselves, economic
recovery will be achieved in a short period of time," he said,
adding that everyone would gain from the economic recovery.
</P>
