<HEADLINE> Sousa Left Dortmund for Inter </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, January 26 (Xinhua) -- Portuguese international
midfielder Paulo Sousa left struggling Borussia Dortmund for
Italy's Inter Milan on Monday.
</P>
